<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yuàn nǐ 迦南836</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yuàn nǐ měi yī tiān dōu méng zhǔ kàn gù, yuàn nǐ měi yī tiān dōu yǒu fù chū.
 yuàn nǐ měi yī tiān xīn zhōng dōu chōng mǎn xǐ lè. yīn wèi yé sū néng ràng nǐ xǐ lè.
 yuàn nǐ de líng hún tǐ dōu méng shén bǎo shǒu. yuàn nǐ de jiǎo bù jǐn jǐn gēn suí zhǔ.
 yuàn nǐ cháng cháng jǐng xǐng, shí shí xiàng shén zàn měi, yuàn zhǔ yǒng yuǎn yǔ nǐ tóng zài.
 yuàn zhǔ yǒng yuǎn yǔ nǐ tóng zài.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>836</hymn_number>
</song>